  "notes": "Captures Shopify 2026-04 behavior for external marketing activity update guardrails: mismatched budget/adSpend currencies, update/upsert attempts to change an existing activity to STOREFRONT_APP, and updating an existing STOREFRONT_APP activity to NEWSLETTER by marketingActivityId. The live conformance shop can create a STOREFRONT_APP activity, but a same-remoteId upsert after that creation resolves as create instead of update there, so the originally-STOREFRONT_APP upsert branch is covered by the same shared update validator in focused runtime tests while the live fixture locks the exact Shopify error code/message for the update path."
